<paragraph id="D526B2C00102B312F76B2BDD69B25812" pageId="212" pageNumber="213">Distribution</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BD31F70210A7D3AA0A5DFDB8A62BAEFB" pageId="212" pageNumber="213">
(Fig. 
<figureCitation id="43EEA314843CD3E5E77C307B080D2F41" captionStart="Figure 187" captionStartId="F187" captionText="Figure 187. Distribution of Conostegia povedae." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.67.6703.figure187" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/96545" pageId="212" pageNumber="213">187</figureCitation>
). Endemic to the remaining primary forest in San Vito de Coto Brus, Puntarenas, Costa Rica at 1100-1200 m elevation.
</paragraph>
<caption id="2E5102D8AB0C4FBD2986665BB05682B2" ID-Zenodo-Dep="974031" doi="10.3897/phytokeys.67.6703.figure187" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/96545" pageId="212" pageNumber="213" start="Figure 187" startId="F187">
